\c 66
\s IN\nd kosi\nd* izagweba izizwe; izabusisa iZiyoni
\p
\v 1 Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Amazulu ayisihlalo sami sobukhosi\x + Seb. 7.49,50. 1 Kho. 8.27. 2 Lan. 6.18. Seb. 7.48. 17.24. Hlab. 11.4.\x*, lomhlaba uyisenabelo senyawo zami\x + 60.13. Mat. 5.35. 1 Lan. 28.2.\x*. Ingaphi leyondlu elizangakhela yona? Njalo ingaphi indawo yami yokuphumula?
\v 2 Ngoba zonke lezizinto isandla sami sazenza\x + Jer. 14.22. Jobe 12.9.\x*, lazo zonke lezizinto zikhona, itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*. Kodwa kulowo ngizakhangela\x + 57.15. 61.1.\x*, kulowo ongumyanga lolomoya odabukileyo\x + Hlab. 34.18.\x*, lothuthumela ngelizwi lami\x + 65.5. Ezra 9.4. 10.3. Zaga 28.14.\x*.
\p
\v 3 Ohlaba inkabi \add unjeng\add*obulala umuntu\x + 1.11. 61.8.\x*; onikela umhlatshelo ngewundlu \add unjeng\add*owephula\x + Eks. 13.13.\x* intamo yenja\x + 2 Sam. 3.8. Fil. 3.2.\x*; onikela umnikelo wokudla \add unjengonikela\add* igazi lengulube; otshisa impepha yesikhumbuzo \add unjeng\add*obusisa isithombe. Yebo, bona bakhethile izindlela zabo\x + 58.13. 65.2.\x*, lomphefumulo wabo uthokoza ngezinengiso zabo.
\v 4 Lami ngizakhetha izigcono zabo\x + 3.4.\x*, ngibehlisele abakwesabayo; ngoba ngabiza, akwaphendula muntu\x + 65.12.\x*; ngakhuluma, akwalalela muntu\x + 65.12.\x*; kodwa benza okubi emehlweni ami\x + 65.12.\x*, bakhetha lokho engingathokozanga ngakho\x + 65.12.\x*.
\v 5 Zwanini ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd*, lina elithuthumela ngelizwi layo\x + 66.5. Ezra 9.4. 10.3. Zaga 28.14.\x*. Abafowenu abalizondayo\x + Mat. 10.22.\x*, abalixotsha ngenxa yebizo lami\x + Luka 6.22.\x*, bathi: Kayidunyiswe iN\nd kosi\x + Jobe 13.8. Joha. 16.2.\x*\nd*; khona sizabona\x + 5.19.\x* intokozo yenu\x + 2 Thes. 1.9,10. Tit. 2.13.\x*; bona-ke bazayangeka.
\v 6 Ilizwi lomsindo elivela emzini\x + 5.14.\x*, ilizwi elivela ethempelini, ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* elibuyisela izinzuzo ezitheni zayo.
