\v 12 Ngoba itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Khangelani, ngizaqhelisa ukuthula\x + 48.18. 60.5.\x* kuye njengomfula, lodumo lwezizwe\x + Isam. 21.24.\x* njengesifula esikhukhulayo\x + 30.28.\x*; khona lizamunya\x + 60.16.\x*, lithwalwe\x + 49.22.\x* enhlangothini\x + 60.4.\x*, lidlaliswe\x + 11.8.\x* emadolweni\x + Jobe 3.12.\x*.
\v 13 Njengalowo unina amduduzayo\x + Gal. 4.26.\x*, ngokunjalo mina ngizaliduduza\x + 51.12.\x*; njalo lizaduduzeka eJerusalema\x + Gal. 4.26.\x*.
\v 14 Lapho libona \add lokhu\add*, inhliziyo yenu izathokoza\x + Joha. 16.22.\x*, lamathambo enu\x + Hez. 37.1-10.\x* ahlume njengohlaza\x + 26.19. Dute. 32.2.\x*; lesandla seN\nd kosi\nd* sizakwaziwa ngasezincekwini zayo, njalo izakuba lolaka ngasezitheni zayo.
\v 15 Ngoba khangela, iN\nd kosi\nd* izafika ngomlilo\x + 9.5. 33.14. 2 Thes. 1.8.\x*, lezinqola zayo\x + Hlab. 68.17. Hab. 3.8.\x* njengesivunguzane\x + 21.1.\x*, ukubuyisela intukuthelo yayo ngokufutheka\x + 59.18.\x*, lokukhuza kwayo ngamalangabi omlilo.
\v 16 Ngoba ngomlilo langenkemba yayo\x + 27.1.\x* iN\nd kosi\nd* izangena ekwahluleleni layo yonke inyama\x + 59.4.\x*, lababuleweyo beN\nd kosi\x + Jer. 25.33. Hlab. 69.26.\x*\nd* bazakuba banengi\x + 66.24. Isam. 19.21.\x*.
\v 17 Labo abazingcwelisayo, bazihlambulule ezivandeni\x + 65.3.\x* ngemva kw\add esihlahla\add* esisodwa esiphakathi\x + Hez. 8.11.\x*, besidla inyama yezingulube\x + 65.4.\x*, lesinengiso, legundwane\x + Levi 11.29.\x*, bazaqedwa kanyekanye\x + Esta 9.28.\x*, itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*.
