\v 18 Ngoba mina \add ngiyayazi\add* imisebenzi yabo lemicabango yabo\x + 65.2.\x*; kuzafika ukuthi ngibuthe zonke izizwe lezinlimi; njalo zizafika, zibone udumo lwami\x + Hlab. 86.9.\x*.
\v 19 Ngizabeka-ke isibonakaliso\x + Luka 2.34.\x* phakathi kwazo, ngithume abaphunyukileyo\x + 45.20.\x* babo baye ezizweni, \add e\add*Tarshishi\x + 1 Kho. 10.22.\x*, iPhuli\x + Jer. 46.9. Hez. 27.10.\x*, leLudi\x + Jer. 46.9. Hez. 27.10.\x*, abadonsa idandili\x + Jer. 46.9. Hez. 27.10.\x*, \add e\add*Thubhali\x + Gen. 10.2. Hez. 27.13.\x*, leJavani\x + Gen. 10.2. Hez. 27.13.\x*, izihlenge ezikhatshana\x + 51.5. Gen. 10.5.\x* ezinga\add k\add*ezwa indumela yami, lezinga\add ka\add*boni udumo lwami; njalo zizamemezela udumo lwami phakathi kwezizwe\x + Mal. 1.11.\x*.
\v 20 Bazaletha-ke\x + 14.2.\x* bonke abafowenu\x + 49.22.\x* \add babe\add* ngumnikelo eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 60.7. Roma 15.16.\x* bephuma kuzo zonke izizwe bephezu kwamabhiza, langezinqola, langamathala, laphezu kwezimbongolo, laphezu kwezinyamazana ezilejubane, entabeni yami engcwele \add e\add*Jerusalema, itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*, njengabantwana bakoIsrayeli beletha umnikelo ngesitsha esihlambulukileyo endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 21 Ngizathatha-ke lakubo babe ngabapristi\x + 61.6.\x* \add njalo\add* babe ngamaLevi, itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 22 Ngoba njengamazulu amatsha lomhlaba omutsha\x + 65.17.\x* engizakwenza kuzakuma phambi kwami, itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*, ngokunjalo inzalo yakho\x + 53.10.\x* lebizo lakho kuzakuma.
