\v 24 Bazaphuma-ke, babone izidumbu zabantu\x + 34.3.\x* abaphambeke bemelene lami; ngoba impethu yabo kayiyikufa\x + Mark. 9.44,46,48.\x*, lomlilo wabo kawuyikucitsha\x + 66.15,16. Jobe 14.22. Isam. 21.8.\x*; njalo bazakuba yisinengiso\x + Dan. 12.2.\x* kuyo yonke inyama.
